        "content": "<p>In Mathlib 3, <code>apply f (λ x, _)</code> worked as <code>refine f (λ x, _)</code>. In Mathlib 4, it works as <code>refine' f _</code>. I fix it by using <code>refine</code> instead of <code>apply</code>.</p>",
